videos.description: With less than two seconds on the shot clock, Tim Hardaway Jr. catches the inbounds pass and throws up a prayer of a shot.
videos.headline: Hardaway nails off-balance 3

videos.description: Sterling Brown and Willie Cauley-Stein get tangled up and DeMarcus Cousins tries to break it up, but gets swatted by Cauley-Stein. Cousins responds with a push of his own and the two are handed technical fouls.
